                {
                  "id": "https://colenda.library.upenn.edu/items/ark:/81431/p3cc0vd5b/manifest/annotation/p3",
                  "type": "Annotation",
                  "motivation": "commenting",
                  "body": {
                    "type": "TextualBody",
                    "value": "<p>regard to that law, I <sic>seen</sic>\n                <persName>Mr Standard</persName><lb/> to day and I had a long talk with<lb/> him on\n                the subject and presented him<lb/> with a copy of the last 'Occident” he<lb/>\n                assures me that he will use his efforts<lb/> to have it modified. I am sure\n                were<lb/> you here and present at the legislature<lb/> you could urge our claims in\n                such lan<lb/>guage before the committees that could<lb/> not be easily\n                mis-understood, would to<lb/> God I had the ability I would do<lb/> my utmost to\n                have things right, as they<lb/> ought to be I feel a great interest in<lb/> the\n                matter and have enlisted many of<lb/>\n                <sic>of</sic> the members of the Legislature from<lb/> time to time in our favour, I\n                wish<lb/> you would write an article relative<lb/> to the matter, and if to the\n                purpose<lb/> I am sure it will have the desired<lb/> effect I will have it published\n                and<lb/> well distributed among the members,<lb/> you know that the petition you\n                wrote<lb/> for me to the common Hall of this city<lb/> was the means of the repeal\n                of the<lb/>\n                <date>Sabbath</date> law of <placeName>Richmond</placeName>, and I am<lb/> sure with\n                a little work we can accomplish<lb/> our end. Truly yours. <hi rend=\"underline\"\n                        ><persName role=\"author\">Jacob Ezekiel</persName></hi></p>\n            <p>Love to sister and all relatives</p>"
                  },
                  "target": "https://colenda.library.upenn.edu/items/ark:/81431/p3cc0vd5b/canvas/p3"
                }
              ]
            }
